room_description:
For years, Brock Lassiter has been collecting evidence to take down Antonio Vitelli, a notorious Chicago mafia kingpin. Handpicked by FBI Director Josh Retsal to be the informant, Brock has hidden the evidence he's collected in a secret safe house. But, its location has been compromised - as well as his cover.
The Mafia is in route to confiscate the incriminating evidence against them and Brock is running for his life. As his trusted friend, you've been asked to retrieve the evidence before the mafia does. Find the evidence and save Brock before it's too late!
